<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<website xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:css="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-css">
  <head>
    <title>Online Game Coaching</title>
    <style>
      <![CDATA[
      body {
        font-family: "FreeMono", "Andale Mono", monospace;
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 800px;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .logo {
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100px;
        fill: #00868C;
      }

      header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .burger-menu {
        display: none;
        flex-direction: column;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .burger-menu div {
        width: 25px;
        height: 3px;
        background-color: #000;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .nav-bar {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-end;
      }

      .nav-bar ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        display: flex;
      }

      .nav-bar ul li {
        margin-right: 10px;
      }

      .nav-bar ul li a {
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .nav-bar ul li a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .nav-bar.active {
        background-color: #00B3BB;
      }

      .content {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .section {
        display: none;
      }

      .section#home {
        display: block;
      }

      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      p {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        text-align: justify;
      }

      ul {
        margin-top: 10px;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      ]]>
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <svg class="logo" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path d="M2.926 2.715V13.4l5.306 3.06V5.785l-5.306-3.07zm0 0M21.074 2.715V13.4l-5.306 3.06V5.785l5.306-3.07zm0 0M12 17.307l5.305-3.07H6.695zm0 0"/>
        <path d="M21.074 14.295L12 19.93l-9.074-5.635-.06-6.649L12 3.196l9.133 4.51zm0 0"/>
        <path d="M2.926 14.295L12 19.93l9.074-5.635v-6.65L12 3.196 2.867 7.706zm0 0"/>
        <path d="M9.855 9.59l-2.125 1.23V5.578l2.125-1.23zm0 0M14.145 9.59l2.11 1.23V5.578l-2.11-1.23zm0 0"/>
        <path d="M12 9.255l2.11 1.23h-4.223zm0 0"/>
        <path d="M9.855 14.65l2.11-1.23v4.242zm0 0"/>
        <path d="M14.145 14.65l-2.125-1.23v4.242zm0 0"/>
        <path d="M12 14.65l-2.11-1.23h4.223zm0 0"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="burger-menu">
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
      </div>
      <nav class="nav-bar">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="#rules">Rules</a></li>
          <li><a href="#prices">Prices</a></li>
          <li><a href="#times">Times</a></li>
          <li><a href="#social">Social</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <content class="content">
      <section class="section" id="home">
        <h1>Online Game Coaching Ethos</h1>
        <p>The games we offer coaching for are Legends of Runeterra and Hearthstone: Heroes of Warcraft. We provide coaching for both Ranked Standard and Normal Standard modes.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="section" id="rules">
        <h2>Rules</h2>
        <p>Ranked Mode: Lost Matches are charged 1.5 Gems/Coins less. Won Matches are charged normally. Extra Bonus from Won Matches is 2 Coins. Extra Bonus from newly acquired Ranked Mode matches is 0.5 Gems.</p>
        <p>Normal Mode: Lost Matches are charged 1 Gem/Coin less. Won Matches are charged 0.5 Gem/Coin less. Extra Bonus from Won Matches is 1 Coin. Extra Bonus from newly acquired Normal Mode matches is 0.5 Coins.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="section" id="prices">
        <h2>Prices</h2>
        <p>The prices for coaching sessions are as follows:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Gem Price: $2 or equivalent</li>
          <li>Coin Price: $2 or equivalent</li>
          <li>Floor Price: 5 Gems or 5 Coins</li>
          <li>Extra Bonus from Won Ranked Mode Matches: 2 Coins</li>
          <li>Extra Bonus from Won Normal Mode Matches: 1 Coin</li>
          <li>Extra Bonus from Newly Acquired Ranked Mode Matches: 0.5 Gems</li>
          <li>Extra Bonus from Newly Acquired Normal Mode Matches: 0.5 Coins</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="section" id="times">
        <h2>Times</h2>
        <p>Newly acquired matches can be performed during GMT 11AM / 7PM.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="section" id="social">
        <h2>Social</h2>
        <p>Required Decks are published on our Social Outlets. Please visit our linktr.ee page for more information.</p>
      </section>
    </content>
    <script>
      <![CDATA[
      const burgerMenu = document.querySelector(".burger-menu");
      const navBar = document.querySelector(".nav-bar");
      const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll(".nav-bar ul li a");
      const sections = document.querySelectorAll(".section");

      burgerMenu.addEventListener("click", () => {
        navBar.classList.toggle("active");
      });

      navLinks.forEach((link) => {
        link.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
          e.preventDefault();
          const target = link.getAttribute("href").substring(1);

          sections.forEach((section) => {
            section.style.display = section.id === target ? "block" : "none";
          });

          navBar.classList.remove("active");
        });
      });
      ]]>
    </script>
  </body>
</website>
